779
00:38:43,074 --> 00:38:46,036
before the game came out were either the people on the

780
00:38:46,036 --> 00:38:48,517
development team or the testers. That's it.

781
00:38:48,657 --> 00:38:52,802
and we shipped the game, it had a lot of issues. And the worst

