00:38:55,686 --> 00:38:57,688
things that we should have caught and we could have easily

784
00:38:57,688 --> 00:39:00,712
done something about if we just knew about them at the time. So

785
00:39:00,712 --> 00:39:04,457
the CIV 4, I want to do it completely differently.

