00:52:20,829 --> 00:52:23,631
And our executive producer at Stardock,

1092
00:52:23,631 --> 00:52:25,431
very politely mentioned like,

1093
00:52:25,431 --> 00:52:27,572
hey, maybe you wanna, we've released the game,

1094
00:52:27,572 --> 00:52:29,173
made some changes, you might wanna check it out.

1095
00:52:29,173 --> 00:52:30,614
And so I think he, I can't, sorry for me to read,

1096
00:52:30,614 --> 00:52:32,474
but I think he came back like eight or nine months later

1097
00:52:32,474 --> 00:52:34,095
and was like, oh, this is great, you fixed everything,

1098
00:52:34,095 --> 00:52:36,516
I love the game, and changed his review.

1099
00:52:36,516 --> 00:52:38,397
So if you take the right attitude toward it,

1100
00:52:38,397 --> 00:52:38,877
I think that could be.

1101
00:52:39,457 --> 00:52:41,138
there's no harm there.

1102
00:52:41,138 --> 00:52:43,100
I mean, sometimes you find someone and clearly

