00:56:25,396 --> 00:56:27,517
All right. So I do want to get to the end here. I think it's

1181
00:56:27,517 --> 00:56:30,199
important to always ask yourself, you know, beyond all

1182
00:56:30,199 --> 00:56:33,021
of this stuff about what the development was like and all

